      "span_text": "In this issue of Neurology ® , the research by Haley et al. [CITATION_1] meets the challenge for methodologic rigor by obtaining an epidemiologically derived sample of stroke survivor and caregiver dyads, following them for 36 months poststroke, and comparing them to a matched noncaregiving group.",
